# Project Context

Learnify AI is a full-stack, AI-native learning platform built with React 19 + TanStack Start + Tailwind CSS v4, deployed on Vercel with Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Storage).

## What we've built

### Existing features (full pages):
- Landing, Login, Signup, Pricing, Public WCMS pages (`/p/$slug`)
- Dashboard, AI Tutor, Course Player, Code Playground, Smart Notes, Community Feed, Coaching Hub, Leaderboard, Wallet, Billing, Certificates, Onboarding Wizard, Product Tours, Blog, Settings
- Creator Studio, Admin Panel (Content Manager, Subscription Analytics)
- CustomVideoPlayer, Interactive 3D Cursor, Premium Animated SVG Illustrations

### Newly built features (added in v3.7.0):
- **Resume Builder** (`/resume-builder`): AI resume generator with PDF/DOCX upload + auto-fill
- **ATS Checker** (`/ats-checker`): ATS score dashboard with keyword analysis
- **Career Roadmap** (`/career-roadmap`): Personalized 6-phase career learning paths
- **Portfolio Builder** (`/portfolio-builder`): Portfolio plan generator with GitHub projects, photo upload, live preview

### New files created:
- `src/routes/_authenticated/resume-builder.tsx`
- `src/routes/_authenticated/ats-checker.tsx`
- `src/routes/_authenticated/career-roadmap.tsx`
- `src/routes/_authenticated/portfolio-builder.tsx`
- `src/lib/resume.functions.ts` — `generateResume`, `checkAtsScore`, `generateCareerRoadmap`, `generatePortfolio`, `extractResumeFields`
- `src/lib/file-parser.ts` — PDF (pdfjs-dist) and DOCX (mammoth) text extraction
- `src/components/ResumeFileUpload.tsx` — shared drag-and-drop file upload component

### Key modifications:
- AppShell nav updated with all 4 new feature nav items + data-tour attributes
- ProductTour updated with portfolio-builder step, all target selectors fixed to specific nav items
- InteractiveDemoCards updated with `route` field linking to actual pages, added Portfolio Builder card
- PWA `sw.js` fixed — was filtering out all static assets due to `url.startsWith("http")` check
- Portfolio Builder field mapping: `summary`→`bio`, `targetRole`→`tagline`, `linkedin`→`socialLinks`
- `pdfjs-dist` worker configured with `workerSrc = ""` to avoid URL resolution issues

### Known issues:
- Auto-fill from uploaded PDF/DOCX not working in Resume Builder and ATS Checker — `extractResumeFields` server function needs debugging (not filling fields automatically after upload)
- The AI server functions (`generateResume`, `checkAtsScore`, etc.) use `user-ai.ts` multi-provider chain (Groq → Gemini → OpenRouter)

### Architecture:
- React 19 + TanStack Start (file-based routing) + Tailwind CSS v4
- TanStack Server Functions for backend (Vercel Edge)
- Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Storage)
- AI: OpenRouter ←→ Gemini ←→ Groq (fallback chain)
- Payments: Cashfree (Subscriptions + Wallet + Payouts)
- Email: Gmail SMTP (primary) ←→ Resend ←→ Brevo
